column2: SELECT up_id, dbo.fGetNearestObjIdEq (up_ra, up_dec, up_sep) as objId FROM #upload WHERE dbo.fGetNearestObjIdEq (up_ra, up_dec, up_sep) IS NOT # SELECT TOP # p.ra, p.dec, cast (str (p.ra, #, #) as float) as ra, cast (str (p.[dec], #, #) as float) as dec, p.u, p.g, p.r, p.i, p.z, p.modelMagErr_u, p.modelMagErr_g, p.modelMagErr_r, p.modelMagErr_i, p.modelMagErr_z, dbo.fIAUFromEq (p.ra, p.[dec]) as SDSSname, IS# (s.spectroFlux_u, #) as spectroFlux_u, IS# (s.spectroSynFlux_u, #) as spectroSynFlux_u, IS# (s.z, #) as redshift FROM ..PhotoObj AS p LEFT OUTER JOIN ..SpecObj s ON p.objID = s.bestObjID JOIN #x AS x ON x.objID = p.objID JOIN #upload AS u ON u.up_id = x.up_id WHERE (p.type = # OR p.type = #) ORDER BY x.up_id
